@startuml
title Camera Discovery and Onboarding

actor Operator
participant Frontend
participant "Control Plane API" as API
participant "Discovery Coordinator" as Discover
participant "ONVIF Probe Worker" as Probe
participant "ONVIF Cameras" as Cameras
participant "Camera Registry" as Registry
participant "Credential Service" as Creds
database "Metadata Store" as Metadata

Operator -> Frontend: Start radar scan
Frontend -> API: Start discovery session
API -> Discover: createDiscoverySession()
Discover -> Probe: run discovery

Probe -> Cameras: WS-Discovery
alt Devices found
  Cameras --> Probe: Candidates
else No devices found
  Probe -> Cameras: Active subnet and endpoint validation
  Cameras --> Probe: Reachable ONVIF-like endpoints
end

Probe --> Discover: Normalized candidates
Discover --> API: discovery results
API --> Frontend: Candidate list

Operator -> Frontend: Select device and enter credentials
Frontend -> API: Validate candidate and credentials
API -> Registry: probe candidate
Registry -> Cameras: Read capabilities and stream profiles
Registry --> API: Normalized sources + capabilities
API --> Frontend: Device capability summary

Operator -> Frontend: Save chosen profile
Frontend -> API: Commit camera
API -> Creds: encrypt credentials
Creds --> API: credentialRef
API -> Registry: save camera + sources + credentialRef
Registry -> Metadata: write Camera and CameraSource records
Registry --> API: committed camera
API --> Frontend: Saved camera

API -> API: Publish fresh worker config snapshot

@enduml
